{"tid":1555851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開]十月一日，覺醒嘅香港人面向旗桿肅立，黑洋紫荊旗徐徐升起，眾人唱嘅係《願榮光歸香港》","createTime":"2019-09-09T13:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T07:22:58.000Z","uid":40121,"like":44,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b2e1298cade2b9ea450c1f4775ff6afb582b1ba9","tid":1555851,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:38:19.000Z","msg":"今日係九月九號，我知而家講十月一號係有啲早<br />\n最近運動焦點似乎好散亂，大家比一個又一個黑警濫權同政府冷暴力激到嘔血<br />\n但係似乎又無咩行動，又或者香港人已經唔知點做，呢啲惡人先會得到應得嘅制裁<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">香港人要點做先可以迎來期望已久嘅自由同正義</span><br />\n<br />\n不論是撤回惡法、獨立調查，還是撤回暴動、釋放義士，甚至是真普選<br />\n我地認為我地應該得到發聲不被打壓嘅權利，我地要求參政嘅權利<br />\n五大訴求嘅核心，從來只有四個字：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins><strong>還政於民</strong></ins></span></span><br />\n但係我地又明白，只要係中港二共打壓之下，香港人永無出頭天<br />\n還政於民嘅前提，就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港自主</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人嘅民族意識已經抬頭，要我地唱番中國國歌認自己係中國人已經無乜可能<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">因此係十月一日，我希望可以有個屬於香港人嘅升旗禮</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n係升旗之後，我地可以<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>朗讀我地對於政治嘅訴求、宣言</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n話比全世界知，香港人為左保護自己嘅文化、民族<br />\n為左香港人應得嘅自由同公義，我地立定決心要奮戰到底<br />\n<br />\n呢個方法可能未必可以對準政權<br />\n非常和理非 甚至係非常無謂<br />\n但係運動去到今時今日，香港人需要呢點鼓舞重振旗鼓<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>重新認識、𨤳清自己嘅追求</ins></strong></span><br />\n接下來先可以係凜冬之中繼續燃燒烈火<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十月一日<br />\n升香港人嘅旗<br />\n唱香港人嘅歌<br />\n讀香港人嘅革命宣言</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n有無手足認同想搞？"},{"pid":"432dca290c0215e1419ae080fcbbbe4ea7fedf4a","tid":1555851,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:38:47.000Z","msg":"自推一下先"},{"pid":"77ee293517680d9ffcc663ab962fd35619b2652c","tid":1555851,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:38:57.000Z","msg":"頭先開錯台"},{"pid":"e59ae42d5ae9b296f1b4646f17875a548b3dddbd","tid":1555851,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:39:18.000Z","msg":"有無手足認同就推下啦"},{"pid":"3cbf805cdd382c4389bcc48443a967978881e0e9","tid":1555851,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:39:44.000Z","msg":"有幾多問題要諗架，例如係邊度搞<br />\n有無樂團幫手"},{"pid":"7d4682cb99da52ab824817fb40556ee340492c75","tid":1555851,"uid":8170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:40:38.000Z","msg":"煙花緊要啲，朝早唔駛搞咁多嘢"},{"pid":"ba8ab54d1ebab6836dfc5c8e35224628e2f2274f","tid":1555851,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:40:49.000Z","msg":"繼續推到大人回為止"},{"pid":"d3a0bbc541ebff0910d2df0d8cea7f6fac84830e","tid":1555851,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:41:05.000Z","msg":"今時今日要有人理真攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e52840a19c4ff9288a2bc1275946b7e0a19ebf5d","tid":1555851,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d4682cb99da52ab824817fb40556ee340492c75","tid":1555851,"uid":8170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:40:38.000Z","msg":"煙花緊要啲，朝早唔駛搞咁多嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:41:34.000Z","msg":"或者929搞都得啊"},{"pid":"0d4e903d027bbff58b55c74ded2eefd8104428c8","tid":1555851,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:41:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08685df84d21fac204ca2b96372d61249c15df79","tid":1555851,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T13:45:34.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"b97f92c1ad01da850248a64